          "debateRelevance": "Useful when debating whether hidden human support is a pragmatic bridge to automation or a deceptive shortcut that exploits trust and labor.",
          "counterargument": "A transitional human-supported phase may help a product reach a genuinely automated future, but that defense only works if transparency and fairness are taken seriously.",
