                  "imageGuidance": "Use /imagesearch to find the exact Will Crawford 1909 image “Surely the world is growing better” from the Library of Congress, Wikimedia Commons, or Theodore Roosevelt Center. This is a known historical image, so do not use /imagecreator as a replacement. Image must be exact and realistic; WSC app mandatory for framing only.",
