          "debateRelevance": "Useful when debating whether prolonged suspension can be meaningful and reflective or whether it mainly becomes sterile, frustrating, and destructive.",
          "counterargument": "Some liminal states create insight, but being trapped in-between can also drain agency, hope, and dignity instead of enriching experience.",
